title: Jenkins and Jonez - Who’s Pettier: Larry Bird or Joel Embiid?

description:
The guys discuss the Most Valuable Booker Boy, the oddly special relationship between James Harden and Daryl Morey, LeBron sort of but not really breaking the scoring record, DeMar DeRozan’s hot streak, more Larry Bird pettiness, Joel Embiid’s twitter mastery, and much more.
